70
00:03:27,354 --> 00:03:28,288
Thank you, Madam.

71
00:03:31,513 --> 00:03:32,448
Miss Banxia.

72
00:03:33,594 --> 00:03:34,560
Please.

73
00:03:39,393 --> 00:03:40,793
Who allowed you to eat with my bowl?

74
00:03:43,233 --> 00:03:44,314
What's all the fuss about?

75
00:03:44,314 --> 00:03:46,393
What's the problem if he uses it?
Hurry up and eat.

76
00:03:46,833 --> 00:03:48,474
I'm not hungry. I'll go to the pharmacy.

77
00:03:49,393 --> 00:03:50,754
It's still early. Why are you rushing

78
00:03:50,754 --> 00:03:51,874
to the pharmacy?

79
00:03:51,874 --> 00:03:52,793
You went the wrong way.

80
00:03:53,354 --> 00:03:54,208
Yes.

81
00:03:54,513 --> 00:03:56,273
Miss Banxia, just eat first.

82
00:03:58,993 --> 00:04:01,474
You wouldn't be cautious

83
00:04:02,154 --> 00:04:03,634
and unwilling to dine with me,
would you?

84
00:04:05,754 --> 00:04:06,673
Shut up.

85
00:04:10,553 --> 00:04:13,113
Mother, I'm going to the pharmacy

86
00:04:13,113 --> 00:04:14,393
to tidy up the herbs.

87
00:04:15,354 --> 00:04:16,256
Well...

88
00:04:16,713 --> 00:04:17,874
Don't save food. I'm not hungry.

89
00:04:20,794 --> 00:04:22,913
What herbs need to be sorted
at the pharmacy?

90
00:04:23,994 --> 00:04:24,960
Are you asking me?

91
00:04:25,434 --> 00:04:26,953
Banxia has left. Why are you still here?

92
00:04:27,994 --> 00:04:29,353
I haven't even picked up the bowl yet.

93
00:04:29,593 --> 00:04:30,674
So what are you waiting for?

94
00:04:36,994 --> 00:04:37,874
Where are Jinrong and Keling?

95
00:04:38,874 --> 00:04:39,776
Still sleeping.

96
00:04:40,473 --> 00:04:42,473
It's so late,
and they're still sleeping?

97
00:04:43,234 --> 00:04:44,114
Don't leave food for them.

98
00:04:44,114 --> 00:04:44,960
Really?

99
00:04:45,353 --> 00:04:46,234
Then I'll eat it, okay?

100
00:04:46,513 --> 00:04:48,033
Mr. Lu, can you finish it?

101
00:04:48,288 --> 00:04:49,184
I can finish it.

102
00:04:49,184 --> 00:04:50,434
Can you eat this much?

103
00:04:51,554 --> 00:04:52,512
Take out some for them.

104
00:04:52,634 --> 00:04:53,568
It's all saved, Mother.

105
00:04:55,794 --> 00:04:56,800
Just eat.

106
00:05:20,554 --> 00:05:21,504
Jinrong,

107
00:05:22,833 --> 00:05:24,074
no one saw you as you came, right?

108
00:05:28,434 --> 00:05:30,033
Was it necessary to make me

109
00:05:30,033 --> 00:05:31,473
enter from the back door?

110
00:05:32,074 --> 00:05:32,994
No, it's not.

111
00:05:35,513 --> 00:05:37,033
I really can't stand this kind of

112
00:05:37,314 --> 00:05:38,794
sneaky life.

113
00:05:40,194 --> 00:05:41,393
Yes, I know, Jinrong.

114
00:05:42,353 --> 00:05:43,833
I know we've been together
for a long time.

115
00:05:44,473 --> 00:05:45,376
But isn't it quite good

116
00:05:45,754 --> 00:05:47,434
for us to drink tea

117
00:05:47,634 --> 00:05:49,353
and chat together?

118
00:05:49,713 --> 00:05:50,593
What's so good about it?

119
00:05:51,473 --> 00:05:52,513
We've been together

120
00:05:52,513 --> 00:05:53,593
for a long time.

121
00:05:53,794 --> 00:05:55,634
And we always hide
in the Spring River Restaurant,

122
00:05:56,033 --> 00:05:57,513
drinking tea.

123
00:05:57,953 --> 00:05:58,994
Don't be mad.

124
00:05:58,994 --> 00:06:00,634
Here. Drink some tea and calm down.

125
00:06:01,634 --> 00:06:03,393
Now, I'm sick at the sight of tea.

126
00:06:03,393 --> 00:06:04,320
Then we're not drinking it.

127
00:06:04,754 --> 00:06:05,600
Have some snacks.

128
00:06:09,314 --> 00:06:11,234
My mother is arranging blind dates
for me now.

129
00:06:11,953 --> 00:06:13,114
Do you think I should go or not?

130
00:06:14,074 --> 00:06:15,593
Y-You definitely can't go.

131
00:06:16,153 --> 00:06:17,273
You are already with me.

132
00:06:17,473 --> 00:06:18,593
And you are seeing other men?

133
00:06:18,593 --> 00:06:19,674
Do you think it's appropriate?

134
00:06:20,513 --> 00:06:21,393
No, it's not appropriate.

135
00:06:21,393 --> 00:06:22,336
It's certainly not.

136
00:06:22,554 --> 00:06:24,833
But how should I tell my mother?

137
00:06:25,353 --> 00:06:27,114
You can just say you don't want to go.

138
00:06:30,353 --> 00:06:31,593
But you know

139
00:06:31,593 --> 00:06:32,593
my mother's temperament.

140
00:06:33,114 --> 00:06:34,048
I wouldn't dare say that.

141
00:06:35,473 --> 00:06:36,416
Why don't you go tell her?

142
00:06:37,593 --> 00:06:38,528
Me?

143
00:06:40,393 --> 00:06:42,754
Will it be appropriate
for me to talk to her?

144
00:06:42,754 --> 00:06:43,994
You should talk to her.

145
00:06:46,114 --> 00:06:47,008
Then how about

146
00:06:47,153 --> 00:06:48,674
I go talk to my mother,

147
00:06:48,794 --> 00:06:49,874
and you go talk to your father?

148
00:06:50,713 --> 00:06:51,616
My father?

149
00:06:54,194 --> 00:06:55,104
Jinrong,

150
00:06:55,554 --> 00:06:56,953
c-can we not bring this up?

151
00:06:56,953 --> 00:06:59,153
Aren't we quite good the way we are now?

152
00:07:01,713 --> 00:07:03,114
Don't be angry.

153
00:07:03,353 --> 00:07:04,224
Here.

154
00:07:04,314 --> 00:07:05,593
Look at this. Look at it.

155
00:07:06,194 --> 00:07:07,074
Do you like it?

156
00:07:07,674 --> 00:07:10,033
Young Lord, I don't want these.

157
00:07:10,314 --> 00:07:12,473
These are not the reasons I am with you.

158
00:07:12,593 --> 00:07:13,953
Tell me what you want.

159
00:07:13,953 --> 00:07:15,153
I can have someone buy it.

160
00:07:15,153 --> 00:07:16,114
I want you to tell others

161
00:07:16,114 --> 00:07:17,234
about our relationship.

162
00:07:19,234 --> 00:07:20,160
Well...

163
00:07:21,754 --> 00:07:23,314
Jinrong,

164
00:07:23,314 --> 00:07:25,033
isn't it enough for the two of us
to be together?

165
00:07:25,033 --> 00:07:26,674
Why do we have to let others know?

166
00:07:26,994 --> 00:07:28,114
Besides, are you with me

167
00:07:28,353 --> 00:07:29,513
just to let others know?

168
00:07:29,513 --> 00:07:30,554
Can't we let others know

169
00:07:30,554 --> 00:07:31,680
that I am with you?

170
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,736
Yes.

171
00:07:32,736 --> 00:07:34,754
Our relationship was unstable
when we were first together.

172
00:07:34,754 --> 00:07:36,554
I understand that you
didn't want to make it public.

173
00:07:36,554 --> 00:07:38,153
But it has been a long time.

174
00:07:38,153 --> 00:07:39,473
Is it going to be like this forever?

175
00:07:39,473 --> 00:07:41,234
Yes, tell me

176
00:07:41,234 --> 00:07:42,153
what you want me to do now.

177
00:07:42,153 --> 00:07:43,314
It's not about what I want now.

178
00:07:43,314 --> 00:07:44,473
It's about what you want.

179
00:07:44,634 --> 00:07:45,504
I...

180
00:07:46,194 --> 00:07:47,874
Okay, l-let's not talk about this.

181
00:07:47,874 --> 00:07:48,896
Let's drop the topic, okay?

182
00:07:49,554 --> 00:07:50,674
Then I have nothing else to say.

183
00:08:05,033 --> 00:08:05,913
Neither do I.

184
00:08:06,513 --> 00:08:07,434
I should go back now.

185
00:08:22,368 --> 00:08:24,608
(Jiren Pharmacy)

186
00:08:27,194 --> 00:08:28,128
Master,

187
00:08:28,674 --> 00:08:29,632
do you have a minute?

188
00:08:29,754 --> 00:08:30,720
Yes. What's the matter?

189
00:08:31,674 --> 00:08:32,554
Master,

190
00:08:32,554 --> 00:08:34,113
I think I've contracted
some kind of disease.

191
00:08:34,593 --> 00:08:35,794
I'm itching all over.

192
00:08:37,633 --> 00:08:39,434
(Ancestral medicine)
It's only natural that a man who lingers

193
00:08:39,434 --> 00:08:40,434
in brothels gets sick.

194
00:08:42,154 --> 00:08:43,136
Well, that's true.

195
00:08:44,274 --> 00:08:45,914
Master, what do you think?

196
00:08:46,233 --> 00:08:47,104
Is my condition severe?

197
00:08:48,394 --> 00:08:49,473
Why are there so many bites?

198
00:08:49,953 --> 00:08:52,434
They are all over your arm.

199
00:08:52,753 --> 00:08:53,914
These are flea bites.

200
00:08:53,914 --> 00:08:54,880
Don't worry.

201
00:08:55,233 --> 00:08:56,096
Fleas?

202
00:08:56,873 --> 00:08:58,074
How can there be fleas?

203
00:08:58,593 --> 00:08:59,794
I'm usually very clean.

204
00:08:59,794 --> 00:09:00,794
I take several baths a day.

205
00:09:01,713 --> 00:09:03,113
Master, can you take another look?

206
00:09:03,914 --> 00:09:05,434
I think there might be more on my back.

207
00:09:07,353 --> 00:09:09,034
People can see us.

208
00:09:09,314 --> 00:09:10,314
Follow me, Mr. Shen.

209
00:09:10,514 --> 00:09:11,456
Please come in.

210
00:09:15,034 --> 00:09:15,904
Be careful.

211
00:09:19,353 --> 00:09:20,993
You look slim when you're dressed.

212
00:09:20,993 --> 00:09:22,194
But you're actually quite muscular.

213
00:09:22,514 --> 00:09:24,674
You have a good figure.

214
00:09:27,194 --> 00:09:28,633
Where have you been?

215
00:09:28,633 --> 00:09:29,873
Why are there so many bites?

216
00:09:30,434 --> 00:09:31,360
Tidy yourself up.

217
00:09:31,674 --> 00:09:32,593
Don't worry.

218
00:09:32,674 --> 00:09:33,554
I'll prescribe you.

219
00:09:34,194 --> 00:09:35,314
One dose is for a bath,

220
00:09:35,593 --> 00:09:37,473
and the other is to be taken orally.

221
00:09:39,434 --> 00:09:40,353
Thank you, Master.

222
00:09:40,473 --> 00:09:41,554
No problem.

223
00:09:41,554 --> 00:09:42,633
How much does this cost?

224
00:09:42,914 --> 00:09:43,808
Two taels.

225
00:09:45,034 --> 00:09:45,920
Two taels?

226
00:09:47,633 --> 00:09:49,833
Banxia, it doesn't cost that much.

227
00:09:50,753 --> 00:09:51,680
Wait.

228
00:09:51,993 --> 00:09:53,314
Two taels are fine.

229
00:09:57,674 --> 00:09:58,674
Master,

230
00:09:58,674 --> 00:10:00,034
I didn't bring money.

231
00:10:00,353 --> 00:10:01,633
Can you put it on my account?

232
00:10:01,833 --> 00:10:02,752
You!

233
00:10:03,713 --> 00:10:05,753
It's okay.
Mr. Shen is a guest of our family.

234
00:10:06,434 --> 00:10:08,794
After the medicine is ready,

235
00:10:08,794 --> 00:10:09,833
I'll let...

236
00:10:09,833 --> 00:10:10,752
I won't go.

237
00:10:12,434 --> 00:10:13,353
I'll send it over to you.

238
00:10:14,873 --> 00:10:15,873
Scald your intimate clothing

239
00:10:15,873 --> 00:10:17,154
with boiling water.

240
00:10:17,394 --> 00:10:18,794
Thank you so much, Master.

241
00:10:23,353 --> 00:10:24,352
Take care.

242
00:10:33,314 --> 00:10:34,304
Don't mind him.

243
00:10:36,074 --> 00:10:37,056
It's okay.

244
00:10:40,674 --> 00:10:41,713
Annoying.

245
00:10:44,633 --> 00:10:46,154
Another tub of water
so early in the morning!

246
00:10:58,674 --> 00:11:00,353
I-I'm sorry.

247
00:11:08,394 --> 00:11:09,873
Are you still angry?

248
00:11:11,713 --> 00:11:13,074
I'm not even angry.

249
00:11:13,074 --> 00:11:15,314
What do you have to be angry about?

250
00:11:15,953 --> 00:11:16,993
Don't be angry.

251
00:11:17,753 --> 00:11:19,233
You can be angry for a while longer.

252
00:11:20,514 --> 00:11:21,408
Feeling better now?

253
00:11:21,674 --> 00:11:22,528
Here.

254
00:11:29,394 --> 00:11:31,154
Is it sweeter than usual?

255
00:11:34,833 --> 00:11:35,776
And you spit the seed.

256
00:11:38,194 --> 00:11:39,072
So you've

257
00:11:39,993 --> 00:11:40,873
prepared all these.

258
00:11:42,593 --> 00:11:43,456
And these.

259
00:11:44,953 --> 00:11:45,794
Are you satisfied?

260
00:11:47,274 --> 00:11:48,256
They are okay.

261
00:11:48,633 --> 00:11:49,914
Just "okay"?

262
00:11:51,434 --> 00:11:53,794
Don't be angry anymore.

263
00:11:54,233 --> 00:11:55,200
How about this?

264
00:11:55,873 --> 00:11:56,832
Yes.

265
00:11:57,353 --> 00:11:58,434
I might be a little grumpy

266
00:11:58,434 --> 00:11:59,394
this morning.

267
00:11:59,394 --> 00:12:00,953
It's because I was anxious,
and those words

268
00:12:00,953 --> 00:12:01,794
jumped out of my mouth.

269
00:12:02,274 --> 00:12:04,074
No, actually,

270
00:12:04,833 --> 00:12:06,194
I also had my faults this morning.

271
00:12:06,914 --> 00:12:07,914
If you realize

272
00:12:07,914 --> 00:12:08,833
you have your faults,

273
00:12:08,833 --> 00:12:10,314
it's something we can talk about.

274
00:12:10,914 --> 00:12:11,776
Pour a glass of wine.

275
00:12:11,776 --> 00:12:12,704
Okay.

276
00:12:15,794 --> 00:12:17,034
Let's finish this glass

277
00:12:17,674 --> 00:12:18,592
and let bygones be bygones.

278
00:12:19,314 --> 00:12:20,192
Okay.

279
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:32,096
Young Lord,

280
00:12:32,753 --> 00:12:33,674
frankly speaking,

281
00:12:34,314 --> 00:12:35,514
