We see each other every day.

571
00:24:38,754 --> 00:24:40,514
How about we let bygones be bygones?

572
00:24:45,234 --> 00:24:46,080
Shen Wangyan,

573
00:24:46,234 --> 00:24:47,393
ever since you came to my house,

574
00:24:47,393 --> 00:24:48,593
I've had an uneasy mind.

575
00:24:48,593 --> 00:24:50,353
An uneasy mind has brought me bad luck.

576
00:24:54,193 --> 00:24:55,353
I will kick you out of my house.

577
00:24:55,353 --> 00:24:56,954
Look at that cheap look of yours.
Go away.

578
00:25:01,754 --> 00:25:02,688
What did I say?

579
00:25:04,224 --> 00:25:06,272
(Lord Ling's Mansion)

580
00:25:08,704 --> 00:25:09,554
Jinrong.

581
00:25:09,554 --> 00:25:10,496
Young Lord.

582
00:25:10,754 --> 00:25:12,153
You're finally here. Today, my father

583
00:25:12,234 --> 00:25:13,514
is having a banquet at home.

584
00:25:13,673 --> 00:25:14,720
Are you confident?

585
00:25:15,593 --> 00:25:16,714
Like holding the handle.

586
00:25:17,353 --> 00:25:18,336
What does that mean?

587
00:25:18,633 --> 00:25:19,616
Okay. Let's go.

588
00:25:19,714 --> 00:25:20,608
Come on.

589
00:25:32,153 --> 00:25:33,024
Your Highness, please.

590
00:25:34,673 --> 00:25:35,552
Good.

591
00:25:35,994 --> 00:25:38,673
Let's have a drink together, then.

592
00:25:42,754 --> 00:25:43,648
Jinrong.

593
00:25:43,794 --> 00:25:45,393
With so many people here,
can you handle it?

594
00:25:46,314 --> 00:25:47,714
- Trust me.
- Good. Good.

595
00:25:47,714 --> 00:25:48,640
I'm sure.

596
00:25:52,153 --> 00:25:55,034
You're quite lucky with ladies, huh?

597
00:25:56,034 --> 00:25:57,024
Father.

598
00:25:58,633 --> 00:25:59,552
Why are you here?

599
00:26:00,256 --> 00:26:01,153
I can see...

600
00:26:01,153 --> 00:26:02,034
So rascal.

601
00:26:04,314 --> 00:26:05,184
This is...

602
00:26:05,954 --> 00:26:08,113
This is the eldest daughter
of the Chuns, Chun Jinrong.

603
00:26:08,474 --> 00:26:09,794
She just dropped by.

604
00:26:10,153 --> 00:26:11,040
The Chuns?

605
00:26:12,833 --> 00:26:14,234
The Chuns related to the Fourth Prince.

606
00:26:16,393 --> 00:26:18,873
Greetings, Your Highness.
I'm Chun Jinrong.

607
00:26:18,873 --> 00:26:19,913
No need for formalities.

608
00:26:20,074 --> 00:26:21,873
We should have known each other
a long time ago.

609
00:26:22,433 --> 00:26:23,456
Yes.

610
00:26:23,633 --> 00:26:25,393
I heard about you
from the Young Lord before.

611
00:26:25,593 --> 00:26:26,633
Now that I've seen you,

612
00:26:26,633 --> 00:26:29,474
I've found that
you really have an impressive demeanor.

613
00:26:29,593 --> 00:26:31,514
You're like a star
descended from heaven.

614
00:26:33,833 --> 00:26:34,873
Your Highness, I'll toast you.

615
00:26:34,873 --> 00:26:36,433
Your Highness, I will also toast to you.

616
00:26:36,633 --> 00:26:37,504
No rush.

617
00:26:37,794 --> 00:26:38,913
Today, I am in a good mood.

618
00:26:39,153 --> 00:26:41,034
Let's take turns.

619
00:26:43,040 --> 00:26:43,994
Chun...

620
00:26:43,994 --> 00:26:44,864
Jinrong.

621
00:26:45,673 --> 00:26:46,592
Make yourself at home.

622
00:26:46,592 --> 00:26:48,074
Make sure to keep her company.

623
00:26:48,593 --> 00:26:49,504
Yes.

624
00:27:02,304 --> 00:27:03,232
How is it?

625
00:27:03,433 --> 00:27:05,474
A good start is half the success.

626
00:27:06,714 --> 00:27:07,648
Like holding the handle.

627
00:27:07,873 --> 00:27:08,832
Great.

628
00:27:12,994 --> 00:27:13,873
Your Highness,

629
00:27:13,873 --> 00:27:15,754
thank you for your generous hospitality.

630
00:27:15,754 --> 00:27:17,754
I have no way to repay you.
I'm willing to dedicate a dance

631
00:27:17,954 --> 00:27:18,873
to express my gratitude.

632
00:27:19,274 --> 00:27:20,754
Good.

633
00:28:22,113 --> 00:28:23,072
Good.

634
00:28:23,153 --> 00:28:24,096
Good.

635
00:28:29,113 --> 00:28:31,554
Let's have another drink.

636
00:28:36,736 --> 00:28:37,696
Good.

637
00:28:37,873 --> 00:28:38,848
Leave.

638
00:28:43,456 --> 00:28:44,448
Father?

639
00:28:47,433 --> 00:28:48,384
You're awake.

640
00:28:51,833 --> 00:28:52,704
Has everyone left?

641
00:28:52,913 --> 00:28:53,760
Yes.

642
00:28:54,234 --> 00:28:56,353
Father, have a cup of tea to sober up.

643
00:28:59,074 --> 00:29:00,234
You rascal.

644
00:29:04,794 --> 00:29:05,728
Father,

645
00:29:05,913 --> 00:29:06,913
actually,

646
00:29:07,873 --> 00:29:09,074
I have something to talk to you.

647
00:29:09,754 --> 00:29:10,656
Go ahead.

648
00:29:11,314 --> 00:29:12,288
I kind of

649
00:29:13,593 --> 00:29:14,714
want to get married.

650
00:29:16,794 --> 00:29:17,696
You've thought it through?

651
00:29:18,474 --> 00:29:19,360
Well,

652
00:29:19,474 --> 00:29:20,633
you're not getting any younger.

653
00:29:21,193 --> 00:29:22,954
Let me help you arrange this afterward.

654
00:29:25,074 --> 00:29:26,514
What kind of girl

655
00:29:26,514 --> 00:29:27,754
do you hope I marry?

656
00:29:29,113 --> 00:29:32,113
I don't have high expectations for you.

657
00:29:32,633 --> 00:29:34,113
You should find

658
00:29:34,393 --> 00:29:36,393
a gentle, kind,

659
00:29:36,994 --> 00:29:38,554
and filial girl, and that's good enough.

660
00:29:39,193 --> 00:29:40,353
That's what I've been thinking.

661
00:29:40,864 --> 00:29:41,728
Father, rest assured.

662
00:29:41,728 --> 00:29:43,552
My future wife and I
will both love and respect you.

663
00:29:44,913 --> 00:29:47,393
Actually, I don't have high expectations
for myself either.

664
00:29:47,913 --> 00:29:50,153
Marrying a commoner's daughter
is enough for me.

665
00:29:50,994 --> 00:29:51,968
That's okay.

666
00:29:53,193 --> 00:29:55,954
A daughter
from a mid-ranking official's family

667
00:29:56,153 --> 00:29:57,034
can also match you.

668
00:29:59,314 --> 00:30:00,224
Father,

669
00:30:00,554 --> 00:30:03,234
what if her family has no official rank?

670
00:30:04,433 --> 00:30:05,514
What do you mean?

671
00:30:05,514 --> 00:30:06,464
For example,

672
00:30:07,314 --> 00:30:08,192
a commoner's family.

673
00:30:09,954 --> 00:30:10,954
Who are you talking about?

674
00:30:11,474 --> 00:30:12,320
No one in particular.

675
00:30:12,794 --> 00:30:13,824
Just, for example,

676
00:30:14,633 --> 00:30:16,833
Chun Jinrong, who just danced.

677
00:30:18,554 --> 00:30:20,034
You want to marry a dancing girl?

678
00:30:20,034 --> 00:30:21,474
No, she's not a dancing girl.

679
00:30:21,474 --> 00:30:23,433
She is Chun Keling's elder sister.

680
00:30:23,433 --> 00:30:25,754
Well, Chun Keling
is the Fourth Prince's woman.

681
00:30:25,754 --> 00:30:27,593
She is kind of connected
to the imperial family, right?

682
00:30:27,794 --> 00:30:29,633
The Fourth Prince is different.

683
00:30:29,633 --> 00:30:30,913
He can do whatever he wants.

684
00:30:30,913 --> 00:30:32,034
Who do you think you are?

685
00:30:32,314 --> 00:30:33,248
Are you a match?

686
00:30:33,474 --> 00:30:35,153
No, is she a match?

687
00:30:35,456 --> 00:30:36,433
She is.

688
00:30:36,433 --> 00:30:37,376
Pah!

689
00:30:39,034 --> 00:30:39,936
Tell you what,

690
00:30:40,193 --> 00:30:41,714
if you dare bring this up again with me,

691
00:30:42,193 --> 00:30:43,074
I'll break your leg.

692
00:30:43,474 --> 00:30:44,352
Father!

693
00:30:44,833 --> 00:30:46,113
Father, please listen to me! Father!

694
00:31:00,994 --> 00:31:01,856
Coming.

695
00:31:08,514 --> 00:31:10,433
Miss Banxia, long time no see.

696
00:31:11,274 --> 00:31:12,256
Mr. Xin.

697
00:31:14,234 --> 00:31:15,104
Please.

698
00:31:19,353 --> 00:31:21,274
Mrs. Chun, thank you
for taking care of this matter.

699
00:31:22,274 --> 00:31:23,353
Don't mention it.

700
00:31:24,754 --> 00:31:25,633
Mrs. Chun, please stay.

701
00:31:26,433 --> 00:31:28,234
We'll meet again.

702
00:31:29,514 --> 00:31:30,633
Mr. Xin, take care.

703
00:31:37,344 --> 00:31:38,304
Mother,

704
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:41,440
what is he here for?

705
00:31:42,433 --> 00:31:43,514
He is here for Mr. Shen.

706
00:31:44,234 --> 00:31:45,153
He said their master

707
00:31:45,153 --> 00:31:46,593
wants to hire Mr. Shen as a tutor

708
00:31:46,994 --> 00:31:47,994
for 20 taels a day.

709
00:31:48,393 --> 00:31:49,248
They want Shen Wangyan?

710
00:31:51,193 --> 00:31:52,034
It seems that Mr. Shen

711
00:31:52,034 --> 00:31:53,353
is really someone.

712
00:31:53,353 --> 00:31:54,193
Puff!

713
00:31:56,673 --> 00:31:57,593
Banxia,

714
00:31:57,593 --> 00:31:59,153
aren't you an educated person?

715
00:31:59,433 --> 00:32:01,113
When did you become so crude?

716
00:32:01,873 --> 00:32:03,314
Mother, let me tell you

717
00:32:03,314 --> 00:32:04,633
what kind of person Shen Wangyan is.

718
00:32:04,913 --> 00:32:06,153
He is just cunning and crafty.

719
00:32:06,393 --> 00:32:07,794
It might be him who invited Mr. Xin.

720
00:32:11,314 --> 00:32:12,160
Chun Banxia,

721
00:32:12,593 --> 00:32:15,113
I noticed that you have been
very critical of Mr. Shen recently.

722
00:32:16,234 --> 00:32:18,274
Well, you saw him...

723
00:32:18,994 --> 00:32:20,314
He hasn't blamed you.

724
00:32:20,314 --> 00:32:21,913
But you are still relentless.

725
00:32:22,234 --> 00:32:24,234
You might let Shen Wangyan go with him

726
00:32:24,234 --> 00:32:25,393
and not stay in our house anymore.

727
00:32:25,393 --> 00:32:26,304
I don't plan to tell him.

728
00:32:26,514 --> 00:32:27,392
You shouldn't, either.

729
00:32:36,274 --> 00:32:37,184
Go.

730
00:32:37,754 --> 00:32:39,274
Go create your own world.

731
00:32:40,474 --> 00:32:41,593
Do you really want me to go?

732
00:32:44,673 --> 00:32:46,873
Mr. Xin said
they would pay you 20 taels a day.

733
00:32:47,673 --> 00:32:48,514
It's 20 taels.

734
00:32:49,193 --> 00:32:50,554
Do you know what that means?

735
00:32:51,193 --> 00:32:52,994
Master couldn't earn that much
in a month.

736
00:32:53,954 --> 00:32:56,153
And Mr. Xin is no ordinary person.

737
00:32:56,514 --> 00:32:58,913
The one he serves must be very powerful.

738
00:32:59,554 --> 00:33:01,153
Don't you need to meet such people?

739
00:33:01,833 --> 00:33:03,034
Aren't you going to file an appeal?

740
00:33:03,954 --> 00:33:05,113
You must have someone support you.

741
00:33:05,792 --> 00:33:06,754
That's right.

742
00:33:06,754 --> 00:33:07,744
Right?

743
00:33:08,393 --> 00:33:09,274
No time to lose.

744
00:33:09,913 --> 00:33:10,913
I'll pack luggage for you.

745
00:33:11,714 --> 00:33:12,640
But

746
00:33:13,714 --> 00:33:14,754
I can't bear to leave you.

747
00:33:15,913 --> 00:33:16,913
Don't push it.

748
00:33:18,336 --> 00:33:19,232
Banxia,

749
00:33:19,994 --> 00:33:21,234
seeing you so reluctant to let me go,

750
00:33:21,673 --> 00:33:23,113
I've decided not to go.

751
00:33:23,593 --> 00:33:24,593
Are you out of your mind?

752
00:33:25,353 --> 00:33:26,794
It's very late now.

753
00:33:27,474 --> 00:33:29,113
Do you plan to stay here for the night?

754
00:33:33,873 --> 00:33:34,794
Leave tomorrow morning.

755
00:33:58,433 --> 00:34:00,353
You've been here since you came back.

756
00:34:01,234 --> 00:34:02,913
You didn't respond when I called you.

757
00:34:03,514 --> 00:34:04,448
What's wrong?

758
00:34:05,873 --> 00:34:07,113
Let me stay alone for a while.

759
00:34:13,113 --> 00:34:14,593
Tell me what's happening.

760
00:34:20,416 --> 00:34:21,312
Mother,

761
00:34:23,514 --> 00:34:25,354
I want to go back to Qing City.

762
00:34:32,914 --> 00:34:33,792
Why?

763
00:34:36,874 --> 00:34:38,593
Mother, can I not get married?

764
00:34:39,914 --> 00:34:41,034
What nonsense are you talking about?

765
00:34:42,673 --> 00:34:44,434
Mother, you're right.

766
00:34:46,034 --> 00:34:48,153
I shouldn't have eyes on my head.

767
00:34:49,994 --> 00:34:51,874
I couldn't see myself clearly.

768
00:34:52,834 --> 00:34:55,434
I'm arrogant and ambitious.

769
00:34:55,994 --> 00:34:56,914
I'm worthless.

770
00:34:57,593 --> 00:34:58,434
I'm old.

771
00:34:59,554 --> 00:35:00,448
What nonsense

772
00:35:01,354 --> 00:35:02,474
are you saying?

773
00:35:02,474 --> 00:35:03,914
What indeed happened to you?

774
00:35:04,832 --> 00:35:05,792
Mother,

775
00:35:07,434 --> 00:35:09,673
His Highness won't let me
be with the Young Lord.

776
00:35:13,233 --> 00:35:15,633
You and the Young Lord?

777
00:35:16,394 --> 00:35:18,593
Sorry, Mother,
I should not have hidden this from you.

778
00:35:24,273 --> 00:35:25,673
We moved to Jianglin

779
00:35:26,313 --> 00:35:27,193
so that you could

780
00:35:27,193 --> 00:35:28,514
marry into good families.

781
00:35:29,474 --> 00:35:30,514
If he's not your Mr. Right,

782
00:35:30,793 --> 00:35:32,273
there are other families.

783
00:35:34,273 --> 00:35:35,313
I used to think

784
00:35:35,313 --> 00:35:37,354
I wanted that kind of life.

785
00:35:37,793 --> 00:35:39,193
But then I realized

786
00:35:40,354 --> 00:35:42,113
the person I've fallen in love with
matters the most.

787
00:35:43,633 --> 00:35:45,313
But we can't be together

788
00:35:46,113 --> 00:35:47,793
just because of
our unequal social status.

789
00:35:50,273 --> 00:35:52,633
You have always been the best.

790
00:35:52,633 --> 00:35:54,554
I even feel the Young Lord
does not deserve you.

791
00:35:57,273 --> 00:35:58,474
Unequal social status

792
00:35:58,474 --> 00:35:59,514
is not your fault,

793
00:36:00,394 --> 00:36:01,313
but theirs.

794
00:36:01,713 --> 00:36:03,313
They missed out
on a good daughter-in-law.

795
00:36:05,354 --> 00:36:06,753
Given your conditions,

796
00:36:07,753 --> 00:36:09,313
you'll definitely
marry into a good family.

797
00:36:12,753 --> 00:36:14,313
Alright, don't cry.

798
00:36:23,168 --> 00:36:26,976
(Jianglin)

799
00:36:28,096 --> 00:36:30,688
(Keep simplicity and nourish the heart)

800
00:36:31,354 --> 00:36:32,224
Mrs. Chun,

801
00:36:33,034 --> 00:36:34,016
farewell.

802
00:36:35,633 --> 00:36:37,034
Didn't you say you weren't leaving?

803
00:36:38,113 --> 00:36:39,954
Your words yesterday

804
00:36:39,954 --> 00:36:41,394
made a lot of sense to me.

805
00:36:41,954 --> 00:36:42,954
I need an appeal to Emperor.

806
00:36:43,514 --> 00:36:44,394
This place is very good.

807
00:36:44,994 --> 00:36:46,394
But I have more important things to do.

808
00:36:47,313 --> 00:36:49,034
You clearly have your eye
on the 20 taels a day.

809
00:36:49,874 --> 00:36:50,848
Chun Banxia,

810
00:36:51,113 --> 00:36:52,313
did you tell Mr. Shen about that?

811
00:36:52,954 --> 00:36:54,554
Mrs. Chun, don't blame Miss Banxia.

812
00:36:55,554 --> 00:36:56,673
She did it for my sake.

813
00:36:57,273 --> 00:36:58,176
After all this time,

814
00:36:58,434 --> 00:36:59,914
I haven't helped you much.

815
00:37:00,434 --> 00:37:01,514
I feel ashamed.

816
00:37:01,514 --> 00:37:02,874
Don't say that.

817
00:37:03,434 --> 00:37:04,994
I'm not stopping you from leaving.

818
00:37:05,273 --> 00:37:06,994
You have your own important matters.

819
00:37:07,514 --> 00:37:09,554
I'm just a little worried about you.

820
00:37:09,954 --> 00:37:12,074
Don't be too aggressive
when you are out there.

821
00:37:13,313 --> 00:37:14,193
Wait a moment.

822
00:37:14,193 --> 00:37:15,753
I'm going to get you some travel money.

823
00:37:17,233 --> 00:37:18,144
- Mother...
- Shut up.

824
00:37:18,914 --> 00:37:20,673
Mrs. Chun, there is no need.

825
00:37:21,834 --> 00:37:22,752
No need for too much.

826
00:37:24,914 --> 00:37:26,793
Shen Wangyan, how can you be so brazen?

827
00:37:26,994 --> 00:37:27,936
You will take the money?

828
00:37:28,313 --> 00:37:29,193
You've seen it.

829
00:37:29,193 --> 00:37:30,633
It's madam
who insisted on giving it to me.

830
00:37:31,593 --> 00:37:33,593
They may not know
what kind of person you are,

831
00:37:33,593 --> 00:37:34,874
but I do.

832
00:37:36,633 --> 00:37:37,994
Miss Banxia,

833
00:37:38,434 --> 00:37:39,328
you know me that well?

834
00:37:41,874 --> 00:37:42,753
Shut up.

835
00:37:45,193 --> 00:37:46,793
Well, I won't tease you anymore.

836
00:37:47,434 --> 00:37:49,474
I owe you an apology.

837
00:37:53,793 --> 00:37:54,673
Miss Banxia,

838
00:37:54,673 --> 00:37:56,153
I've met many educated people,

839
00:37:56,793 --> 00:37:58,113
but not many are as stubborn

840
00:37:58,874 --> 00:37:59,753
as you.

841
00:37:59,753 --> 00:38:00,954
I knew you would say that.

842
00:38:01,954 --> 00:38:03,793
People who pride themselves
on being high lack passion.

843
00:38:04,153 --> 00:38:05,914
Those who are tactical lack backbone.

844
00:38:07,034 --> 00:38:08,394
You are just perfect.

845
00:38:09,273 --> 00:38:10,514
You have principles for the world

846
00:38:10,673 --> 00:38:11,874
and a passion for life.

847
00:38:12,233 --> 00:38:13,088
You are quite adorable.

848
00:38:16,514 --> 00:38:18,034
What tricks are you trying to play now?

849
00:38:18,034 --> 00:38:19,434
What tricks can I play?

850
00:38:19,834 --> 00:38:22,354
It has always been you
taking advantage of me, hasn't it?

851
00:38:23,394 --> 00:38:24,288
